## Next Steps
[Agreed next steps, timeline, and next meeting date if set]

## Competitive Intelligence
[Any mentions of competitors, alternative solutions the customer is evaluating, or comparisons made. If none, write "None mentioned".]

## Key Topics
[List 3-7 main themes from the meeting]
